import React from 'react'
import { Spinner, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Loader = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Button variant="primary" disabled>
    <Spinner
      as="span"
      animation="grow"
      size="sm"
      role="status"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    Loading...
  </Button>
        </>
    )
}

export default Loader
